title: (Tues Early Bird) What’s the Haps: Bobby Had A Unique Concert Experience and Amy Got Food Poisoning + Morgan Watches Austin Powers For the First Time and Reviews It

description:
We catch up on our lives with What’s the Haps! Morgan was born in 1993 and we have been giving her TV shows and Movies we thought were awesome back in the day to see if they still hold up. This week, she reviews Austin Powers from 1997.
